# Skill Router

When a task matches a pattern below, read the corresponding SKILL.md **before** starting work. Complete every step in that skill (including tests, route registration, RBAC, data-testid) **without asking the user for confirmation**. See `agent-os/rules/agent-behavior.mdc` for the no-confirmation rule. Skills contain step-by-step instructions, conventions, and checklists specific to this project.

